# Wildheart Style System

## Color System

### Primary Colors
- Primary: `$color-primary` (#5A67D8)
- Primary Light: `$color-primary-light` (lighten 10%)
- Primary Dark: `$color-primary-dark` (darken 10%)

### Accent Colors
- Accent: `$color-accent` (#F6AD55)
- Accent Light: `$color-accent-light` (lighten 10%)
- Accent Dark: `$color-accent-dark` (darken 10%)

### Semantic Colors
- Success: `$color-success` (#48BB78)
- Warning: `$color-warning` (#ECC94B)
- Error: `$color-error` (#F56565)
- Info: `$color-info` (#4299E1)

### Neutral Colors
- White: `$color-white` (#FFFFFF)
- Black: `$color-black` (#000000)
- Gray Scale: 50-900 (from lightest to darkest)

### Glassmorphism Colors
- Background: `$color-bg` (rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8))
- Background Dark: `$color-bg-dark` (rgba(30, 30, 30, 0.8))
- Surface: `$color-surface` (rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3))
- Border: `$color-border` (rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1))
- Shadow: `$color-shadow` (rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05))

## Typography

### Font Families
- Base: `$font-family-base` ('Inter', 'Roboto', sans-serif)
- Heading: `$font-family-heading` ('Inter', 'Roboto', sans-serif)

### Font Sizes
- Base: `$font-size-base` (16px)
- Small: `$font-size-sm` (14px)
- Large: `$font-size-lg` (18px)
- Extra Large: `$font-size-xl` (20px)
- 2XL: `$font-size-2xl` (24px)
- 3XL: `$font-size-3xl` (30px)
- 4XL: `$font-size-4xl` (36px)
- 5XL: `$font-size-5xl` (48px)

### Line Heights
- Base: `$line-height-base` (1.6)
- Heading: `$line-height-heading` (1.2)

## Spacing

### Spacing Scale
- Extra Small: `$spacing-xs` (0.25rem / 4px)
- Small: `$spacing-sm` (0.5rem / 8px)
- Medium: `$spacing-md` (1rem / 16px)
- Large: `$spacing-lg` (1.5rem / 24px)
- Extra Large: `$spacing-xl` (2rem / 32px)
- 2XL: `$spacing-2xl` (3rem / 48px)
- 3XL: `$spacing-3xl` (4rem / 64px)

## Border Radius

### Border Radius Scale
- Small: `$border-radius-sm` (4px)
- Medium: `$border-radius-md` (8px)
- Large: `$border-radius-lg` (12px)
- Extra Large: `$border-radius-xl` (16px)
- 2XL: `$border-radius-2xl` (24px)
- Full: `$border-radius-full` (9999px)

## Shadows

### Shadow Scale
- Small: `$shadow-sm` (0 1px 2px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05))
- Medium: `$shadow-md` (0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06))
- Large: `$shadow-lg` (0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 4px 6px -2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05))
- Extra Large: `$shadow-xl` (0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 10px 10px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04))
- 2XL: `$shadow-2xl` (0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25))

## Transitions

### Transition Speeds
- Fast: `$transition-fast` (0.15s ease)
- Base: `$transition-base` (0.3s ease)
- Slow: `$transition-slow` (0.5s ease)

## Z-index

### Z-index Scale
- Dropdown: `$z-index-dropdown` (1000)
- Sticky: `$z-index-sticky` (1020)
- Fixed: `$z-index-fixed` (1030)
- Modal Backdrop: `$z-index-modal-backdrop` (1040)
- Modal: `$z-index-modal` (1050)
- Popover: `$z-index-popover` (1060)
- Tooltip: `$z-index-tooltip` (1070)

## Breakpoints

### Breakpoint Scale
- Extra Small: `$breakpoint-xs` (0)
- Small: `$breakpoint-sm` (576px)
- Medium: `$breakpoint-md` (768px)
- Large: `$breakpoint-lg` (992px)
- Extra Large: `$breakpoint-xl` (1200px)
- 2XL: `$breakpoint-2xl` (1400px)

## Component Guidelines

### Buttons
- Use `.btn` class for all buttons
- Variants: primary, secondary, success, danger, warning, info
- Outline variants available with `.btn-outline-*` classes
- Sizes: default, small (`.btn-sm`), large (`.btn-lg`)
- Block buttons with `.btn-block`
- Icon buttons with `.btn-icon`
- Loading state with `.btn-loading`

### Forms
- Form groups with `.form-group`
- Form controls with `.form-control`
- Validation states: `.is-valid`, `.is-invalid`
- Checkboxes and radio buttons with `.form-check`
- Input groups with `.input-group`
- Floating labels with `.form-floating`

### Cards
- Base card with `.card`
- Card header with `.card-header`
- Card body with `.card-body`
- Card footer with `.card-footer`
- Card variants: primary, secondary, success, danger, warning, info
- Special effects: hover, glass, gradient, accent

